## 2026-04-08 — Session 1

**Tasks completed:** T001, T002, T003, T004, T005, T006 (partial), T010, T016

**Summary:**
Bootstrapped the entire EmpireOS project from scratch. No prior game/ directory existed.

**Files created:**
- `game/CLAUDE.md` — coding standards and architecture guide
- `game/.intel/roadmap.md` — 6-phase roadmap (T001–T024)
- `game/.intel/tasks.json` — full task backlog with priorities
- `game/.intel/execution.log` — this log
- `game/index.html` — entry point with HUD, tab bar, content panels
- `game/styles/main.css` — full dark-theme CSS (BEM, CSS custom properties)
- `game/src/main.js` — boot sequence, save/load, control binding
- `game/src/core/state.js` — central state object and initState()
- `game/src/core/events.js` — pub/sub bus with Events constants
- `game/src/core/tick.js` — 250ms game loop with registerSystem()
- `game/src/core/actions.js` — buildBuilding, demolishBuilding, trainUnit, addMessage
- `game/src/systems/resources.js` — recalcRates(), resourceTick(), training queue
- `game/src/systems/research.js` — startResearch(), researchTick()
- `game/src/ui/hud.js` — 6-resource HUD bar
- `game/src/ui/buildingPanel.js` — grid of building cards with build/demolish
- `game/src/ui/messageLog.js` — scrolling event log
- `game/src/ui/researchPanel.js` — tech tree with progress bar
- `game/src/ui/tabs.js` — Buildings / Research / Log tab switcher
- `game/src/data/buildings.js` — 12 buildings with full stat definitions
- `game/src/data/units.js` — 4 units (soldier, archer, knight, mage)
- `game/src/data/techs.js` — 6 technologies with prerequisite graph
- `game/src/utils/logger.js` — debug logger (no-op in production)
- `game/src/utils/fmt.js` — fmtNum(), fmtRate(), fmtTime()

**Architecture decisions:**
- Vanilla ES modules, no build step — opens directly in browser
- 250ms tick loop (4 ticks/s) with pluggable system registration
- Single state object, all mutations via actions.js
- Pub/sub events decouple systems from UI
- 15% per-building cost scaling for build inflation
- Save/load via localStorage with auto-save every 60s

**Next session should tackle:**
- T007: Canvas map grid (20×20) with fog of war
- T008: Combat resolution engine
- Military unit training UI panel (tab in sidebar)

